com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.read

Interface TableReader

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SubTableReader
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSubTableReader, AbstractTableReader, CsvTableReader, DbfTableReader, DelimitedTextTableReader, ExcelTableReader, FileTableReader, FixedWidthTextTableReader, TextFileTableReader, WhitespaceDelimitedTextTableReader

    public interface TableReader
    The TableReader interface is used to read table data from external data sources. From this table data, DataTable object can be created. There is no restriction on the external data source, so long as the required table data can be formed for access.
